message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories as it proposes a deep learning system for lung cancer detection and diagnosis. The use of convolutional neural networks and model uncertainty also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NEURON). Additionally, the application of the system to medical imaging data indicates a potential fit for the medical imaging (cs.MED) category.
